#: ../../user_manual/selections.rst:17
msgid "Selections"
msgstr "Výbery"

#: ../../user_manual/selections.rst:19
msgid ""
"Selections allow you to pick a specific area of your artwork to change. There"
" are many selection tools available that select in different ways. Once an"
" area is selected, most tools will stay inside that area. On that area you"
" can draw or use gradients to quickly get colored and/or shaded shapes with"
" hard edges."
msgstr ""

